\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\"><code>scroll</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectstart_event\"><code>selectstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Das Ereignis <code>readystatechange</code> wird ausgelöst, wenn sich die Eigenschaft <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a> eines&nbsp;Dokumentes verändert hat.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"allgemeine_information","title":"Allgemeine Information","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"spezifikation\">Spezifikation</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/dom.html#current-document-readiness\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"schnittstelle\">Schnittstelle</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Event</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"aufsteigend\">Aufsteigend</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Nein</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"abbrechbar\">Abbrechbar</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Nein</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"ziel\">Ziel</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Dokument</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"standardaktion\">Standardaktion</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Keine</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// als Alternative zu DOMContentLoaded</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onreadystatechange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>readyState <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"interactive\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">initApplication</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser-kompatibilität","title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Ereignis wird vom Internet Explorer schon sehr lange unterstützt und kann daher als Alternative zum&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/DOMContentLoaded_event\"><code>DOMContentLoaded</code></a>-Ereignis genutzt werden (vgl. Anmerkung&nbsp;[2] im Abschnitt&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/DOMContentLoaded_event#browserkompatibilit%c3%a4t\">Browserkompatibilität</a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"verwandte_ereignisse","title":"Verwandte Ereignisse","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/DOMContentLoaded_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">DOMContentLoaded (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/readystatechange_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">readystatechange (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">load (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">beforeunload (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">unload (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Allgemeine Information","id":"allgemeine_information"},{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"},{"text":"Verwandte Ereignisse","id":"verwandte_ereignisse"}],"summary":"Das Ereignis readystatechange wird ausgelöst, wenn sich die Eigenschaft readyState eines Dokumentes verändert hat.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document: readystatechange event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"readystatechange","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document: readystatechange イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document: readystatechange event","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"readystatechange","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"readystatechange","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Document: readystatechange 事件","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/document/readystatechange_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/document/readystatechange_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/readystatechange_event","title":"readystatechange"}],"pageTitle":"readystatechange - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}